000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ea645bf8c26b31e23f693422ba2360a2a6d33b","tid":1617924,"uid":21849,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:57:25.000Z","msg":"輸入預設的 SIM PIN。<br />\n<br />\n注意，不少電訊供應商，均預設為 1234 或 8888 或 0000 或 1111。但考慮到輸錯三次密碼會鎖卡，而重置卡密碼要花時間或花金錢，所以如果你在第一次輸入 PIN 時，先在 1234 或 8888 或 0000 或 1111 當中選一組，最多只試一次或兩次，如果不對，就不要再嘗試，直接打給電訊公司查詢。<br />\n<br />\n以下資料，只供參考。預設 PIN：<br />\n<br />\n自由鳥：1234<br />\n1010：0000<br />\n3 香港：8888<br />\n數碼通香港：1234<br />\n澳門 CTM：1111<br />\n之後選擇「更改 PIN」。"},{"pid":"919a944b357243403b044713d57ccfd2b7943593","tid":1617924,"uid":21849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:58:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd62f48863fbb721ee2c994af647e7bc0bd2610f","tid":1617924,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e07d56f3720ccaf90bd9c0d5fa14337630ebd4","tid":1617924,"uid":134116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"067b6191d5d4745f43f69a033c62c53c9a6e9b7d","tid":1617924,"uid":295444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d2f3f3dc1ec9740bea9fb38d7fb7157f4d3221a","tid":1617924,"uid":21849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:52:05.000Z","msg":"<strong>方法：設定 - 流動網絡 - SIM PIN - 選擇開啟 SIM PIN。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假如你的手機<span style=\"color: red;\"> SIM 卡沒有上鎖</span>，萬一有人檢獲你的手機，即使你的手機本身有密碼，但<span style=\"color: red;\">匪徒(黑警)只需要把 SIM 卡取出</span>，就能<span style=\"color: red;\">接收訊息</span>。若然你主要的<span style=\"color: red;\">通訊軟件或社交媒體帳號，都是綁定了該手機號碼，而你又從來沒